:Class Stark
вЌќ Fastify-style HTTP router for Dyalog APL, built on top of Jarvis.
вЌќ
вЌќ Usage:
вЌќ   routerв†ђвЋ•NEW Stark
вЌќ   router.Handlersв†ђmyAppNS
вЌќ   router.Get  '/users'      'ListUsers'
вЌќ   router.Get  '/users/{id}' 'GetUser'
вЌќ   router.Post '/users'      ('CreateUser' opts)   вЌќ opts is an APLAN ns with metadata
вЌќ   router.Start 8080

    :Field Public  Handlers      вЌќ namespace where handler functions live
    :Field Public  ThreadModeв†ђ'' вЌќ DYALOG_JARVIS_THREAD: '' (Jarvis default), 0, 1, 'DEBUG', 'AUTO'
    :Field Public  Info          вЌќ namespace with title, version, description for OpenAPI info
    :Field Private _routes       вЌќ vector of route descriptor namespaces
    :Field Private _jarvis       вЌќ underlying Jarvis instance

    в€‡ Make0
      :Access Public
      :Implements Constructor
