    вЌќ в”Ђв”Ђ Route registration: one method per HTTP verb в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
    вЌќ
    вЌќ Dyadic: path on left, right is either 'handlerName' or ('handlerName' opts)
    вЌќ   path router.Get 'HandlerName'
    вЌќ   path router.Get ('HandlerName' opts)

    в€‡ {r}в†ђpath Get rarg
      :Access Public Instance
      rв†ђ_Register 'GET' path rarg
    в€‡

    в€‡ {r}в†ђpath Post rarg
      :Access Public Instance
