    в€‡

    в€‡ {r}в†ђpath Put rarg
      :Access Public Instance
      rв†ђ_Register 'PUT' path rarg
    в€‡

    в€‡ {r}в†ђpath Delete rarg
      :Access Public Instance
      rв†ђ_Register 'DELETE' path rarg
    в€‡

    в€‡ {r}в†ђpath Patch rarg
