    вЌќ в”Ђв”Ђ Internal registration в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

    в€‡ {r}в†ђ_Register(method path rarg);handler;options
      :Access Private Instance
      :If 1в‰ в‰Ўrarg                           вЌќ nested: ('HandlerName' options)
          (handler options)в†ђrarg
      :Else
          handlerв†ђrarg                     вЌќ simple string
          optionsв†ђ()
      :EndIf
      rв†ђ(
        method: method
        pattern: ,path
        handler: handler
        options: options
      )
      _routes,в†ђr
    в€‡

    вЌќ в”Ђв”Ђ Path matching в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
    вЌќ
    вЌќ pattern pathMatch path в†’ (matched pathParams)
    вЌќ Compares a pattern like '/users/{id}' against a path like '/users/42'.

    pathMatchв†ђ{
        patSplit pathSplitв†ђ'/'(в‰ вЉ†вЉў)ВЁвЌє вЌµ
        pathSplitв‰ўвЌҐв‰ўpatSplit:0()
        varMaskв†ђ'{'=вЉѓВЁpatSplit
        в‰ў/(вЉ‚~varMask)/ВЁpatSplit pathSplit:0()
        namesв†ђ({1в†“ВЇ1в†“вЌµ}ВЁpatSplit[вЌёvarMask])
        1(()вЋ•VSETв†“вЌ‰в†‘names(pathSplit[вЌёvarMask]))
    }

    вЌќ в”Ђв”Ђ Dispatch в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
    вЌќ
    вЌќ Routes an incoming Jarvis request to the matching handler.

    в€‡ resultв†ђ_Dispatch req;routes;r;matched;pp
      :Access Public Instance
      routesв†ђ((вЋ•CВЁ_routes.method)в€ЉвЉ‚вЋ•C req.Method)/_routes
      :For r :In routes
          (matched pp)в†ђr.pattern pathMatch req.Endpoint
          :If matched
              req.PathParamsв†ђpp
              req.QueryParamsв†ђ(вЋ•NS '')вЋ•VSET{(,вЉѓвЌµ)(2вЉѓвЌµ)}ВЁв†“req.QueryParams
              :If '_'=вЉѓr.handler
                  resultв†ђ(вЌЋr.handler)req          вЌќ internal handler (on Stark)
              :Else
                  resultв†ђ(HandlersвЌЋr.handler)req   вЌќ user handler
              :EndIf
              :Return
          :EndIf
      :EndFor
      req.Fail 404
      resultв†ђвЋ•NS ''
      result.detailв†ђ'Not Found'
    в€‡

    вЌќ в”Ђв”Ђ OpenAPI spec generation в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

    в€‡ rв†ђOpenAPI
      :Access Public Instance
      rв†ђ_BuildOpenAPI
    в€‡

    в€‡ resultв†ђ_OpenAPIHandler req
      :Access Public Instance
      resultв†ђ_BuildOpenAPI
    в€‡

    в€‡ specв†ђ_BuildOpenAPI;paths;r;pathKey;pathNS;method;op;opts;segs;varMask;param;pNS;ct;code;schemaNS;e;respNS;respKey;ctKey
      :Access Private Instance
      вЌќ 0(7162вЊ¶) mangles strings into valid APL names; вЋ•JSON demangles them back
      specв†ђвЋ•NS ''
      spec.openapiв†ђ'3.0.3'
      spec.infoв†ђInfo
      ctKeyв†ђ0(7162вЊ¶)'application/json'

      pathsв†ђвЋ•NS ''
      :For r :In _routes
          :If '_'=вЉѓr.handler в‹„ :Continue в‹„ :EndIf   вЌќ skip internal routes

          вЌќ Get or create path object
          pathKeyв†ђ0(7162вЊ¶)r.pattern
          :If 0=paths.вЋ•NCвЉ‚pathKey
              pathsвЋ•VSET вЉ‚pathKey ()
          :EndIf
          pathNSв†ђpaths вЋ•VGET pathKey

          вЌќ Build operation object
          methodв†ђвЋ•C r.method
          opв†ђвЋ•NS ''
          op.parametersв†ђвЌ¬
          op.responsesв†ђвЋ•NS ''

          вЌќ Extract path parameters from {param} segments
          segsв†ђ'/'(в‰ вЉ†вЉў)r.pattern
          varMaskв†ђ'{'=вЉѓВЁsegs
          :For param :In {1в†“ВЇ1в†“вЌµ}ВЁvarMask/segs
              pNSв†ђ(name: param в‹„ in: 'path' в‹„ required: (вЉ‚'true') в‹„ schema: (type: 'string'))
              op.parameters,в†ђвЉ‚pNS
          :EndFor
          :If 0=в‰ўop.parameters в‹„ op.вЋ•EX'parameters' в‹„ :EndIf

          вЌќ Map metadata from route options
          optsв†ђr.options
          :If 9=вЋ•NC'opts'
              :If 2=opts.вЋ•NC'summary'     в‹„ op.summaryв†ђopts.summary         в‹„ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.вЋ•NC'description'  в‹„ op.descriptionв†ђopts.description  в‹„ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.вЋ•NC'tags'         в‹„ op.tagsв†ђopts.tags                в‹„ :EndIf

              вЌќ Request body schema
              :If 9=opts.вЋ•NC'body'
                  ctв†ђ() вЋ•VSET вЉ‚ctKey (schema: opts.body)
                  op.requestBodyв†ђ(required: (вЉ‚'true') в‹„ content: ct)
              :EndIf

              вЌќ Success response: (statusCode schema)
              :If 2в‰¤opts.вЋ•NC'response'
                  (code schemaNS)в†ђopts.response
                  ctв†ђ() вЋ•VSET вЉ‚ctKey (schema: schemaNS)
                  respNSв†ђ(description: 'Successful response' в‹„ content: ct)
                  respKeyв†ђ0(7162вЊ¶)вЌ•code
                  op.responses вЋ•VSET вЉ‚respKey respNS
              :EndIf

              вЌќ Error responses: vector of (statusCode description) pairs
              :If 2в‰¤opts.вЋ•NC'errors'
                  :For e :In opts.errors
                      respKeyв†ђ0(7162вЊ¶)вЌ•вЉѓe
                      op.responses вЋ•VSET вЉ‚respKey (description: 2вЉѓe)
                  :EndFor
              :EndIf
          :EndIf

          вЌќ Default 200 response if none specified
          :If 0=в‰ўop.responses.вЋ•NL ВЇ2 ВЇ9
              respKeyв†ђ0(7162вЊ¶)'200'
              op.responses вЋ•VSET вЉ‚respKey (description: 'Successful response')
          :EndIf

          pathNS вЋ•VSET вЉ‚method op
      :EndFor

      spec.pathsв†ђpaths
    в€‡

